{
  "stem": "11641.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 20.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to Brunnlitz-- first we stepped in-- sort of stepped in, quote, unquote, to Gross-Rosen concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because this was the main headquarters of the area where Brunnlitz belonged to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you want to use the word hell on earth, this was a place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was hell on earth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't let us do anything there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave us breakfast about 2 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They gave us lunch about 7 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And by 10 o'clock, you think you were done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You slept this way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's how you had to sleep-- really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You couldn't stretch yourself out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But thank God we were not there too long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were there about five or six days, if I remember correctly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because they knew that we are only temporary, so they gave us as much problems as possible.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we all-- nobody died from our group over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we saw atrocities over there-- unbelievable-- unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The other people that were there-- whatever we saw was--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] We-- we saw-- one person flipped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I never saw it before-- really, in all the years that you would normally-- you would think that people will flip, really.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw, over there, one guy flip-- completely flipped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was talking irrationally-- entirely irrationally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took him away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I understand that they killed him eventually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they killed him, because-- he wasn't from our group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was from-- from different groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And their-- their foremens over there was a lot of Poles, a lot of Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were sadists-- all of them-- very sadistics.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were-- they-- they, you know, they behaved over there, and we-- we couldn't wait.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They stripped us, first of all, naked-- all completely naked.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
